/** @page guides User Guides

Task-oriented recipes and reference material that complement the
[API reference](modules.html). Each guide distills the most frequently asked
questions from the upstream issue tracker into a single, self-contained page.

@par Get answers
- @subpage faq &mdash; mirrored images, IR emitter, log spam, timestamps,
  color/depth synchronization.
- @subpage configuration &mdash; the `Config` struct, environment variables,
  and color-camera controls.

@par Work with the data
- @subpage registration &mdash; map between color, depth, and 3-D coordinates;
  build point clouds.
- @subpage depth_accuracy &mdash; systematic offset, warm-up drift,
  calibration limits, and how to correct them.

@par Integrate
- @subpage recording_replay &mdash; capture raw streams, replay them through
  any pipeline, and run multiple Kinects.
- @subpage webcam &mdash; bridge the RGB stream into apps that expect a system
  webcam.
- @subpage python &mdash; the community Python bindings and the two most common
  recipes.

@par Maintain
- @subpage self_hosted_runner &mdash; set up the self-hosted macOS GitHub
  Actions runner that powers CI (build, tests, sanitizers, Metal parity).

*/
